{"tid":560141,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"港航俾你$19,999*起（經濟艙）或$45,999*起（商務艙）一口氣買起最多510套來回香港同日韓^嘅機票","createTime":"2018-02-13T23:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T12:07:08.000Z","uid":65328,"like":5,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3574192f4d25a1c9a817720e14769afdf6a6fb","tid":560141,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:32:20.000Z","msg":"個個都拍拖，唔通個個都想拍住拖去旅行？其實一個人話飛就飛咪仲開心！<br />\nHong Kong Airlines情人節前夕特別呈獻「一人盡情飛」日韓通Pass，俾你$19,999*起（經濟艙）或$45,999*起（商務艙）一口氣買起最多510套來回香港同日韓^嘅機票！啲機票仲係全年不限出發日期同免費更改出發日子添㗎（個別艙位數量有限，先到先得) ！ Fortune Wings Club會員專享，價格優惠加上限定發售，出左雙糧逗完利是梗係要快啲買！<br />\n <br />\n於以下旅行社獨家發售：<br />\n東瀛遊 康泰旅行社 安運滿FUN遊 專業旅運 中國旅行社 南華(快捷)旅行社 安達旅運 百福飛龍旅遊 西敏旅行社<br />\n <br />\n發售日期：即日至2018年3月31日<br />\n旅遊日期：即日至2019年3月31日<br />\n <br />\n*以上價格為機票套票建議售價，並不包括燃油附加費、航空公司及旅行社行政費、附加費、政府及機場稅項及其他收費。產品最終價格視乎個別旅行社而定。<br />\n^航點包括日本東京、大阪、沖繩、札幌、米子、岡山、宮崎、鹿兒島及韓國首爾。<br />\n<br />\nBest part about being a solo traveller is that you&rsquo;ll never need to wait for any replies! Just a right click and you&rsquo;re good to set off! The &ldquo;Unbound 1&rdquo;, brought to you by Hong Kong Airlines on the &ldquo;Pre-Valentine&rsquo;s Day&rdquo;, is your best option getting 510 sets of round trip tickets to Japan or South Korea^ at just $19,999* (Economy Class) or $45,999* (Business Class)!<br />\n <br />\nBetter still, you can choose to take off all year round, with no limitation or whatsoever anytime you need to change the flight time (limited seats available to certain flights and on a first-come, first-served basis)! The Unbound 1 is an exclusive special offer for Fortune Wings Club members! Hurry and cash in your bonus and red pockets for the flight tickets!<br />\n <br />\nAvailable at the following travel agencies:<br />\nEGL Tours, Hong Thai Travel, Wincastle Travel, Travel Expert, China Travel Service, Nan Hwa(Express) Travel Service, Westminster Travel, Citizen Thunderbird Travel and Lotus Tours<br />\n<br />\nBooking period: from today until 31 Mar 2018<br />\nTravel period: from today until 31 Mar 2019<br />\n<br />\n*The suggested retail prices above do not include any fuel surcharges, taxes and charges of airline, travel agents, government and airports. Retail prices of travel agents shall be final.<br />\n^Destinations include Tokyo, Osaka, Okinawa, Sapporo, Yonago, Okayama, Miyazaki, and Kagoshima in Japan and Seoul in South Korea.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/073137_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F14%2F073137_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b007c70b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2de655b1a01e045e8a0d5c48e782989ee4c472b8","tid":560141,"uid":31841,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:35:50.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係好唔掂<br />\n開始撲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06602c62f42f5201d796130fb662861305a35a45","tid":560141,"uid":34140,"like":29,"dislike":25,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:36:32.000Z","msg":"自己一個去已經夠毒，仲要去500幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe6c86f158e72d3f0b551409f755d6736c9b7b8","tid":560141,"uid":4285,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:38:34.000Z","msg":"我諗起樂視執前果d 一世任睇 plan <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3741157ff0640c4ec99d8b3cd4385cbf34b4512","tid":560141,"uid":97710,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:39:04.000Z","msg":"睇黎就爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ffcd7867d0a89114bbfb74dc67520d548a147a","tid":560141,"uid":2697,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T23:39:18.0